@@ -0,0 +1,21 @@
+html.lenis
+  height auto
+
+.lenis.lenis-smooth
+  scroll-behavior auto
+
+.lenis.lenis-smooth [data-lenis-prevent]
+  overscroll-behavior contain
+
+.lenis.lenis-stopped
+  overflow hidden
+
+.lenis.lenis-scrolling iframe
+  pointer-events none
+
+.splide.is-initialized:not(.is-active) .splide__list
+  display flex !important
+  gap 2rem
+
+.testimonials__slider .splide__track
+  overflow visible

commits.content:
html.lenis
  height auto

.lenis.lenis-smooth
  scroll-behavior auto

.lenis.lenis-smooth [data-lenis-prevent]
  overscroll-behavior contain

.lenis.lenis-stopped
  overflow hidden

.lenis.lenis-scrolling iframe
  pointer-events none

.splide.is-initialized:not(.is-active) .splide__list
  display flex !important
  gap 2rem
